body:
1. Early game ganks have been severely hurt because junglers can no longer pick up {{item:3706}} {{item:3715}} on first back since it now costs {{item:1039}} + 700 gold as opposed to {{item:1039}} + 450 Gold before.

2. Hunters talisman feels non-existant on {{champion:32}} and I would think it would be most helpful on him but apparently I can&#039;t sustain enough mana to kill 2 camps without going oom. I would much rather have no talisman and my jungle item upon my first back rather than having to invest in 2 jungle items to finally build my {{item:3706}}. 



I know total gold has been increased and jungle monsters gold too, but with {{item:3709}} TOTAL COST 2250 gold &rArr; 2625 gold it hits junglers hard early game since they still don&#039;t get enough gold compared to laners and now I feel like junglers are even more behind especially Tank junglers with slow clears. {{champion:33}} {{champion:54}} {{champion:57}} {{champion:106}}
